---
import { cfImageUrl, CF_IMAGES } from '../config/site';
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background image overlay -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 z-0"
    style={`background-image: url('${cfImageUrl(CF_IMAGES.heroImageId)}'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;`}
  >
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-950/90 via-zinc-950/80 to-zinc-950"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/4 -left-32 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-red-600/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>
  <div
    class="absolute bottom-1/4 -right-32 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-amber-600/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-32 text-center">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[4px] text-red-400 font-extrabold mb-6">The Label They Invented Is Now Our Badge</p>

    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl tracking-tight mb-8 leading-[0.95]">
      <span class="islamophobe-gradient">ISLAMOPHOBE</span><span class="text-white">.ME</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-zinc-300 font-semibold max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4 leading-snug">
      Sharia Law Will Never Be Compatible With Western Values.
    </p>

    <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-red-400 font-bold max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-snug">
      Child Marriage Will Never Be Accepted.
    </p>

    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-zinc-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      The label they invented to silence normal human revulsion is now our badge.
      America and the West were built to protect the vulnerable, not to import 7th-century rules that sexualize them.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="#manifesto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 px-8 py-4 bg-red-700 hover:bg-red-600 text-white font-extrabold rounded-2xl transition-colors text-lg">
        Read the Case
      </a>
      <a href="#take-action" class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 px-8 py-4 border border-red-700 text-red-400 hover:bg-red-950/50 font-extrabold rounded-2xl transition-colors text-lg">
        Take Action
      </a>
      <button
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 px-8 py-4 border border-zinc-700 text-zinc-300 hover:bg-zinc-900 font-extrabold rounded-2xl transition-colors text-lg"
        onclick="navigator.share({ title: document.title, url: window.location.href }).catch(() => {})"
      >
        Share This Site
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
